PrecisRegulations Amending the MARIHUANA EXEMPTION (FOOD AND DRUGS ACT) REGULATIONS by exempting the marihuana produced by "designated-person production licence holders" from the requirements of the Food and Drugs Act and its regulations in order to permit them to be remunerated for the production activities.
